          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This number must follow the regular expression ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "-?[0-9]+(\\.[0-9][0-9])?",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ". The amount is required and can’t be empty. ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You specify the currency for the entire transaction including line items by setting the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/applepaypaymentrequest/1916118-currencycode",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " property in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/applepaypaymentrequest",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If the payment request is for an automatic reload payment, the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "amount",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " indicates the reload payment amount authorized when the account drops below the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
